item.title: Compiling problem
item.dc:creator: @Phineas Phineas
item.description:
@Phineas wrote:

Put this code in your compiler

@echo off Title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_##\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

“##”= Your version of JDK.
